  typingSpeed: 0.05
  dialogueLines:
  - "Khoan\u2026 \xC1nh s\xE1ng g\xEC v\u1EADy? Kh\xF4ng gi\u1ED1ng \xE1nh n\u1EAFng.
    Kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i l\u1EEDa."
  - "M\xECnh ch\u01B0a t\u1EEBng th\u1EA5y n\xF3 tr\u01B0\u1EDBc \u0111\xE2y\u2026
    t\u1EEB trong r\u1EEBng s\xE2u? K\u1EF3 l\u1EA1 qu\xE1."
  - "Ch\u1EC9 c\u1EA7n nh\xECn nhanh th\xF4i. Kh\xF4ng \u0111i xa \u0111\xE2u\u2026
    M\u1EB9 s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt \u0111\xE2u."
